== Report bugs/file tickets ==

  1. [http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/search Search the bugtracker] for any existing tickets that are similar to the ones you are planning to file. 
    * You can also use [https://www.google.com/ Google] with your search query followed by the `site:http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/ticket` parameter.

  2. If you didn't find an existing ticket, discuss it with the [http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/wiki/TwistedCommunity#TwistedCommunity Twisted Community].
      
  3. Now, follow these steps to file a ticket:
    * [/register Register] on this site.
    * [http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/wiki/TwistedDevelopment#FilingTickets file a ticket].



